{"title":"Signature Sauces","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"buffalo-sauce","title":"Buffalo Sauce","description":"\u003cp\u003eOur take on a traditional Buffalo hot sauce, a combination of flavour and spice, this zingy sauce is the pairing your chicken has been waiting for.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eHeat Level: 🌶️🌶️🌶️\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eGoes great with:\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eChicken, Burgers, Fries\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"300ml","offers":[{"title":"300ml","offer_id":43005417947365,"sku":"SCB","price":2.9,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0645\/6197\/1429\/products\/Buffalosauce.jpg?v=1654551868"},{"product_id":"mango-habanero-sauce","title":"Mango Habanero Sauce","description":"\u003cp\u003eA combination of fruity and spicy, this hot sauce is one of our favourites; bringing subtle tropical mango flavours and a sweet zing to any meal.  \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eHeat Level: 🌶️🌶️\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eGoes great with:\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eChicken, Fish, Fries\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"300ml","offers":[{"title":"300ml","offer_id":43005421486309,"sku":"","price":2.9,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0645\/6197\/1429\/products\/MangoHabanerosauce.jpg?v=1654548420"},{"product_id":"sweet-lemon-sauce","title":"Sweet Lemon Sauce","description":"\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eFor those that love a bit of sweet and sour, with subtle hints of lemon this sauce packs the perfect combination to have you smackin your lips and keep going for more. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eHeat Level: 🌶️\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eGoes great with:\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eChicken, Fish, Fries\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"300ml","offers":[{"title":"300ml","offer_id":43005405167845,"sku":"","price":2.